  "description": "<p>Enjoy POC\u2019s industry-leading comfort and safety, without breaking the bank. For trail riders that that don't need an NFC chip or Recco reflector in their helmet, the Axion Race is a solid choice. Based in Sweden, POC has been making cutting edge personal safety equipment for snowsports and cycling for nearly two decades.</p><ul><li>MIPS Integra (Multi-directional Impact Protection System) reduces rotational forces in an oblique impact. Moving pads instead of moving liner provide the protection of a standard MIPS liner, but takes up less space and allows more ventilation</li><li>Break-away brim helps absorb impact, decreasing the force that makes it to you, like a crumple zone in a car</li><li>Brim leaves room for goggles, sunglasses, or even an action camera</li><li>Adjustable fit system lets you dial in your perfect fit</li><li>Extended protection wraps around the base of the skull</li><li>Lightweight straps are easy to adjust, and super comfy</li><li>Lots of vents help you keep a cool head, pulling air in the front and letting it exhaust out the back</li></ul>",
